General.Name: ThinTech Materials Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: ThinTech Materials Technology Co., Ltd. designs, manufactures, and sells alloys and optoelectronics materials in Taiwan, Mainland China, Japan, Europe, and North America. Its products include sputtering targets for flat panel display planar, optical data storage, decorative and functional coating, passive component, optical element, and semi-conductive; and thin film targets for solar cell applications. The company also offers flat panel display rotary sputtering targets; nickel alloy c-hook for coil wire pickling; sputtering target bonding services; precious metal refining and sales services; analytical services; and metal powder for 3D printing, as well as acid and alkali-resistance alloy, and titanium for cooking/tableware. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Kaohsiung, Taiwan.
